<template>
	<dl>
		<dt>ID</dt>
		<dd>{{tuser.id}}</dd>
		<dt>name</dt>
		<dd>{{tuser.name}}</dd>
		<dt>pass</dt>
		<dd>{{tuser.pass}}</dd>
		<dt>jointime</dt>
		<dd>{{tuser.jointime}}</dd>
	</dl>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios';

export default {
	data: function () {
		return {
			tuser: {}
		}
	},
	created () {
		axios
		.get(`/api/v1/tusers/${this.$route.params.id}.json`)
		.then(response => (this.tuser = response.data))
	}
}
</script>

<style scoped>
</style>
